mg src=\"https://nume.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Screen-Shot-2020-05-25-at-1.11.03-pm-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnume.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2FScreen-Shot-2020-05-25-at-1.11.03-pm-1.png&h=e48825de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e67221cc2c0d288924c265acb16cad838482f072","tid":2121264,"uid":38218,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"n Ben 轉玩屎眼"},{"pid":"6d3e3d3b5b23de1ab4282721386373b07ab54f16","tid":2121264,"uid":99700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DG4fUKB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDG4fUKB.jpg&h=0a591f87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43d276cd19541f4d0ebf801893cd477d13ea472b","tid":2121264,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e67221cc2c0d288924c265acb16cad838482f072","tid":2121264,"uid":38218,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"n Ben 轉玩屎眼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:07:57.000Z","msg":"九巴放針案 判案書全文(案件編號：DCCC 80/2019)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744151</a><br />\n<blockquote>法醫的專家意見<br />\n11. 警方取得法醫傅家聰的專家意見，關於案中所插縫紉針可能造成的風險及相關併發症，他的意見如下：<br />\n(i) 預計盆骨區及大腿後側位置下面的皮膚及軟組織或器官會受傷；<br />\n(ii) 接近皮膚的男性及女性泌尿生殖及腸胃結構有可能因穿透性傷害而受傷，該些傷勢可引致痛楚、局部感染、出血造成血腫、血尿、血精及便血；<br />\n<span class=\"red\">(iii) 一些肛門附近的主要盆壁肌肉可能受傷，該些肌肉對控制排泄十分重要，若因深層穿透受傷，可導致大小便失禁；</span><br />\n(iv) 泌尿生殖及腸胃結構中帶有多條細小分支的神經，若因表面穿透受損，可引致皮膚感覺麻木或變弱，深層穿透可能引致更大範圍的骨盆肌肉感覺變弱，該些肌內對控制膀胱及腸道十分重要。<span class=\"red\">重要神經結構若被深層穿透，可引致某程度性功能障礙；</span><br />\n(v) 大腿位置可能受傷，造成痛楚、出血可能造成血腫及局部感染等併發症。若穿透明顯深至大腿內部位置，則有可能傷及坐骨神經，可能引致無力屈膝、足部無力活動、足部難以向內彎或向下彎，影響步態及平衡；<br />\n(vi) 異物穿透均存在感染風險；<br />\n(vii) 兒童受害人由於身體較小，傷勢預計會比較嚴重及深層；年老受害人免疫系統較弱，預計需要更長時間從併發症中康復。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"99ae73fdcba73cd90bb140f7e58cad9c75f4e3b7","tid":2121264,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:18:42.000Z","msg":"2020-07-21<br />\n「巴士再生夢」九巴捐贈巴士予路德會聖十架學校<br />\n九龍巴士（一九三三）有限公司（「九巴」）透過舊巴士及退役巴士捐贈計劃，在七月向路德會聖十架學校捐贈退役巴士。<br />\n<br />\n學校將退役巴士命名為「芬蘭號」，名字源於該校師生在三年多前已開始到訪芬蘭作交流，芬蘭教育強調讓每一個小孩公平受教，鼓勵孩子主動想、主動問、主動找答案。為了將當地教育元素引入香港，學校決定向九巴申請退役巴士，增加校舍空間，有助實現「芬蘭教育夢」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.kmb.hk/lib/_W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kmb.hk%2Flib%2F_W.jpg&h=2df48a27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df00376cf20d9bf422ca7cbe63ed5d9c51c7cce6","tid":2121264,"uid":92401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dea0fa652e09116f4e4d3d1c271208ef30cc2144","tid":2121264,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:02:24.000Z","msg":"以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nume.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Nume-TM1015-SS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnume.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FNume-TM1015-SS.jpg&h=50497f05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nume.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/WhatsApp-Image-2020-05-13-at-10.20.40-AM-2-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnume.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-05-13-at-10.20.40-AM-2-1.jpeg&h=3c271c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nume.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/xScreen-Shot-2020-02-21-at-8.06.16-pm.png.pagespeed.ic.y530kNdxUH.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnume.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FxScreen-Shot-2020-02-21-at-8.06.16-pm.png.pagespeed.ic.y530kNdxUH.webp&h=5ca6e45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nume.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/WhatsApp-Image-2020-05-06-at-10.27.50-AM-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2