，深層穿透可能引致更大範圍的骨盆肌肉感覺變弱，該些肌內對控制膀胱及腸道十分重要。<span class=\"red\">重要神經結構若被深層穿透，可引致某程度性功能障礙；</span><br />\n(v) 大腿位置可能受傷，造成痛楚、出血可能造成血腫及局部感染等併發症。若穿透明顯深至大腿內部位置，則有可能傷及坐骨神經，可能引致無力屈膝、足部無力活動、足部難以向內彎或向下彎，影響步態及平衡；<br />\n(vi) 異物穿透均存在感染風險；<br />\n(vii) 兒童受害人由於身體較小，傷勢預計會比較嚴重及深層；年老受害人免疫系統較弱，預計需要更長時間從併發症中康復。</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:01:14.000Z","msg":"孫銘謙巴打咁好記性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45326d72a867c65a6f04febee0c62e024167f86","tid":2121264,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"曼德拉效應"},{"pid":"22a085f45bce110def79fc3670df2387f7ef6315","tid":2121264,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"734b6a9b321129a0b64a7cccaf9917ad0c48b1a2","tid":2121264,"uid":159333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:00:29.000Z","msg":"自己封自己做X神... 好柒呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de3a516964e1c33e67215aa2a5dbadbd444d39d","tid":2121264,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b45326d72a867c65a6f04febee0c62e024167f86","tid":2121264,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"曼德拉效應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2hHnShg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2hHnShg.gif&h=b6e62c8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e92097c920a15404f90aa2afa53290d050b335dc","tid":2121264,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"n賓粒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.